      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": false,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": false,
        "liquid": "<style>\n  .trustpilot-reviews-section {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    padding: 20px;\n    background-color: #fff0de;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n\n  .trustpilot-summary {\n    flex-basis: 20%;\n    text-align: left;\n  }\n\n  .trustpilot-summary h2 {\n    font-size: 24px;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n\n  .trustpilot-stars img {\n    width: 100px;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n\n  .trustpilot-logo {\n    width: 50px; /* Taille réduite */\n    margin-top: 10px;\n  }\n\n  .review-carousel {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-basis: 75%;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n\n  .review-card {\n    width: 270px;\n    padding: 15px;\n    margin-right: 15px;\n    background-color: #fbeedb;\n    border: 1px solid #eaeaea;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n    transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n\n  .review-card:hover {\n    transform: scale(1.05);\n  }\n\n  .review-card img {\n    width: 70px;\n  }\n\n  .review-card p {\n    margin: 5px 0;\n    font-size: 14px;\n  }\n\n  .review-card strong {\n    font-weight: bold;\n  }\n\n  .nav-arrow {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 50%;\n    transform: translateY(-50%);\n    background-color: #f6f1e6;\n    border: 2px solid #ddd;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    width: 40px;\n    height: 40px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: background-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n  }\n\n  .nav-arrow:hover {\n    background-color: #f6f1e6;\n    box-shadow: 0 6px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n  }\n\n  .arrow-left {\n    left: -20px; \n  }\n\n  .arrow-right {\n    right: -20px; \n  }\n\n  .nav-arrow::before {\n    content: '';\n    display: block;\n    border: solid #333;\n    border-width: 0 3px 3px 0;\n    padding: 5px;\n  }\n\n  .arrow-left::before {\n    transform: rotate(135deg);\n  }\n\n  .arrow-right::before {\n    transform: rotate(-45deg);\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .trustpilot-reviews-section {\n      flex-direction: column;\n      padding: 10px;\n    }\n\n    .trustpilot-summary {\n      flex-basis: 100%;\n      text-align: center; \n      margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .trustpilot-stars img {\n      width: 80px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n    }\n\n    .trustpilot-logo {\n      width: 80px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n    }\n\n    .review-carousel {\n      flex-basis: 100%;\n      overflow-x: auto;\n      padding-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n\n    .review-card {\n      min-width: 85%;\n      margin-right: 10px;\n    }\n\n    .nav-arrow {\n      display: none;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"trustpilot-reviews-section\">\n  <div class=\"trustpilot-summary\">\n    <h2>Excellent !</h2>\n    <div class=\"trustpilot-stars\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0891/0028/8264/files/stars-5.svg?v=1727197779\" alt=\"5 stars rating\">\n    </div>\n    <p>Basé sur plus de 13,450 avis</p>\n    <img class=\"trustpilot-logo\" src=\"https://companieslogo.com/img/orig/TRST.L_BIG-743be58a.png?t=1720244494\">\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"review-carousel\" id=\"review-carousel\">\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0891/0028/8264/files/stars-5.svg?v=1727197779\" alt=\"5 stars rating\">\n      <p><strong>Vérifié</strong></p>\n      <p></p>\n      <p>Ça fonctionne très bien et je ne l'utilise pratiquement plus juste 2 jours et les aboiements intempestifs c'est fini. Je ne suis absolument pas contre les aboiements mais un de mes chiens regarde la télé et aboie quand il y a des animaux même dans un dessin animé.</p>\n      <p><strong>Pascale C. – Paris, France</strong> - 23/01/2025</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0891/0028/8264/files/stars-5.svg?v=1727197779\" alt=\"5 stars rating\">\n      <p><strong>Vérifié</strong></p>\n      <p>Livraison rapide, excellente qualité</p>\n      <p>La commande a été livrée très rapidement et la qualité de l'AlphaBar est vraiment top. Une mention spéciale pour le packaging super bien fait.</p>\n      <p><strong>Amanda R. – Los Angeles, CA</strong> - 23/08/2024</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0891/0028/8264/files/stars-5.svg?v=1727197779\" alt=\"5 stars rating\">\n      <p><strong>Vérifié</strong></p>\n      <p>Leur produit est une vraie plus-value</p>\n      <p>Je comprends maintenant pourquoi elle fait autant parler d’elle. Bravo pour cette innovation, elle mérite clairement son succès ici à Miami.</p>\n      <p><strong>Mike S. – Brooklyn, NY</strong> - 13/02/2025</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <button class=\"nav-arrow arrow-left\" onclick=\"scrollReviews(-1)\"></button>\n  <button class=\"nav-arrow arrow-right\" onclick=\"scrollReviews(1)\"></button>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  const reviewCarousel = document.getElementById('review-carousel');\n\n  function scrollReviews(direction) {\n    const scrollAmount = 320;\n    reviewCarousel.scrollBy({ left: direction * scrollAmount, behavior: 'smooth' });\n  }\n\n  // Auto-scroll toutes les 3 secondes\n  let autoScrollInterval = setInterval(() => {\n    scrollReviews(1);\n  }, 3000);\n\n  // Stop auto-scroll quand l'utilisateur interagit\n  document.querySelectorAll('.nav-arrow').forEach(arrow => {\n    arrow.addEventListener('click', () => {\n      clearInterval(autoScrollInterval);\n    });\n  });\n</script>",
        "background": "",
        "background_gradient": "",
        "text_color": ""
      }
    },
